002package com.commercetools.api.models.shopping_list;
003
004import com.commercetools.api.models.Referencable;
005import com.commercetools.api.models.ResourceIdentifiable;
006
007public interface ShoppingListMixin extends Referencable<ShoppingList>, ResourceIdentifiable<ShoppingList> {
008    @Override
009    public default ShoppingListResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier() {
010        return ShoppingListResourceIdentifier.builder().id(getId()).build();
011    }
012
013    @Override
014    public default ShoppingListReference toReference() {
015        return ShoppingListReference.builder().id(getId()).build();
016    }
017}
